description: Due to our increasing awareness of the vital significance of fruits and veggies in our diets, you’ll find the culinary masters behind Butcher’s Daughter taking their cleavers to beets, rather than meats. This traveling Juice Bar/Cafe/Vegetable Slaughterhouse is nourishing the bodies and minds of LA with their deliciously nutritious vegan and gluten free Juices, Sandwiches, and Salads- all crafted from 100% organic and locally sourced produce. When it comes to health and beauty, Butcher’s Daughter absolutely cuts it.
name: The Butcher's Daughter
